03}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The fact that this was a criminal situation and it was being dealt with by the courts, we could not intervene or take action until we were presented with the full facts.\", \"from\": 4323, \"to\": 4492, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The fact\", \"from\": 4323, \"to\": 4331}, {\"ngram\": \"a criminal situation\", \"from\": 4346, \"to\": 4366}, {\"ngram\": \"the courts\", \"from\": 4398, \"to\": 4408}, {\"ngram\": \"action\", \"from\": 4441, \"to\": 4447}, {\"ngram\": \"the full facts\", \"from\": 4477, \"to\": 4491}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a matter of hours, actually, we had dealt with that issue within hours of receiving that information and I think that's credit to the team.'\", \"from\": 4493, \"to\": 4640, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a matter\", \"from\": 4500, \"to\": 4508}, {\"ngram\": \"hours\", \"from\": 4512, \"to\": 4517}, {\"ngram\": \"that issue\", \"from\": 4547, \"to\": 4557}, {\"ngram\": \"hours\", \"from\": 4565, \"to\": 4570}, {\"ngram\": \"that information\", \"from\": 4584, \"to\": 4600}, {\"ngram\": \"credit\", \"from\": 4620, \"to\": 4626}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 4630, \"to\": 4638}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On whether White could ever make a return to the tour, he added: 'At this stage he's been completely removed.\", \"from\": 4642, \"to\": 4751, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4653, \"end\": 4658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_people\", \"score\": 0.6097905896054157, \"rank\": 0.6399060507463553, \"text\": \"White\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a return\", \"from\": 4675, \"to\": 4683}, {\"ngram\": \"the tour\", \"from\": 4687, \"to\": 4695}, {\"ngram\": \"this stage\", \"from\": 4711, \"to\": 4721}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the criminal justice system, the system would say there is a right to rehabilitate but we as a sport will take our own view at the time.'\", \"from\": 4752, \"to\": 4892, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the criminal justice system\", \"from\": 4755, \"to\": 4782}, {\"ngram\": \"the system\", \"from\": 4784, \"to\": 4794}, {\"ngram\": \"a right\", \"from\": 4814, \"to\": 4821}, {\"ngram\": \"a sport\", \"from\": 4848, \"to\": 4855}, {\"ngram\": \"our own view\", \"from\": 4866, \"to\": 4878}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 4882, \"to\": 4890}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the current contract for the Crucible to host the World Championship only running until 2027, talk of the tournament's future is as loud as ever.\", \"from\": 4894, \"to\": 5044, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the current contract\", \"from\": 4899, \"to\": 4919}, {\"ngram\": \"the Crucible\", \"from\": 4924, \"to\": 4936}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Championship\", \"from\": 4945, \"to\": 4967}, {\"ngram\": \"talk\", \"from\": 4993, \"to\": 4997}, {\"ngram\": \"the tournament's future\", \"from\": 5001, \"to\": 5024}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Discussions continue over the World Championships and all I can say is those discussions are extremely healthy and there is a great deal of good will on all sides,' said Ferguson of talks with decision-makers in Sheffield.\", \"from\": 5046, \"to\": 5269, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5217, \"end\": 5225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ferguson_unrest\", \"score\": 0.9999999991987352, \"rank\": 8.013109977353262e-10, \"text\": \"Ferguson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ferguson_unrest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ferguson_unrest\"}, {\"begin\": 5259, \"end\": 5268, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheffield\", \"score\": 0.9999999999922693, \"rank\": 7.563565848174153e-12, \"text\": \"Sheffield\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheffield\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheffield\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Discussions\", \"from\": 5047, \"to\": 5058}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Championships\", \"from\": 5073, \"to\": 5096}, {\"ngram\": \"those discussions\", \"from\": 5118, \"to\": 5135}, {\"ngram\": \"a great deal\", \"from\": 5171, \"to\": 5183}, {\"ngram\": \"good will\", \"from\": 5187, \"to\": 5196}, {\"ngram\": \"all sides\", \"from\": 5200, \"to\": 5209}, {\"ngram\": \"talks\", \"from\": 5229, \"to\": 5234}, {\"ngram\": \"decision-makers\", \"from\": 5240, \"to\": 5255}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked if there have been offers from elsewhere, he said: 'Of course!\", \"from\": 5271, \"to\": 5339, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"offers\", \"from\": 5296, \"to\": 5302}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have had offers to move the World Championships many times.\", \"from\": 5340, \"to\": 5402, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"offers\", \"from\": 5352, \"to\": 5358}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Championships\", \"from\": 5367, \"to\": 5390}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Sheffield is a great city, great atmosphere, great history, that's what we export all over the world.\", \"from\": 5403, \"to\": 5508, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5407, \"end\": 5416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheffield\", \"score\": 0.9999999999922693, \"rank\": 7.563565848174153e-12, \"text\": \"Sheffield\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheffield\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheffield\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a great city\", \"from\": 5420, \"to\": 5432}, {\"ngram\": \"great atmosphere\", \"from\": 5434, \"to\": 5450}, {\"ngram\": \"great history\", \"from\": 5452, \"to\": 5465}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 5498, \"to\": 5507}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am a big fan of Sheffield and the Crucible.\", \"from\": 5509, \"to\": 5554, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5527, \"end\": 5536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheffield\", \"score\": 0.9999999999922693, \"rank\": 7.563565848174153e-