a.org/resource/Ferguson_unrest\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some moves\", \"from\": 5813, \"to\": 5823}, {\"ngram\": \"the next year\", \"from\": 5829, \"to\": 5842}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2032 bid time\", \"from\": 5874, \"to\": 5891}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The bid process takes a very long time.\", \"from\": 5913, \"to\": 5953, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The bid process\", \"from\": 5914, \"to\": 5929}, {\"ngram\": \"a very long time\", \"from\": 5936, \"to\": 5952}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'There is only one thing holding an Olympic bid back for snooker and that is that the internationally recognised federation is full of politics.\", \"from\": 5955, \"to\": 6099, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"only one thing\", \"from\": 5965, \"to\": 5979}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic bid\", \"from\": 5988, \"to\": 6002}, {\"ngram\": \"snooker\", \"from\": 6012, \"to\": 6019}, {\"ngram\": \"the internationally recognised federation\", \"from\": 6037, \"to\": 6078}, {\"ngram\": \"politics\", \"from\": 6090, \"to\": 6098}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We walked away from it in fear of reputational damage.\", \"from\": 6100, \"to\": 6154, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fear\", \"from\": 6126, \"to\": 6130}, {\"ngram\": \"reputational damage\", \"from\": 6134, \"to\": 6153}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We were involved in the body that is responsible for Olympic bids for many years, on and off, but not now.\", \"from\": 6155, \"to\": 6261, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the body\", \"from\": 6175, \"to\": 6183}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic bids\", \"from\": 6208, \"to\": 6220}, {\"ngram\": \"many years\", \"from\": 6225, \"to\": 6235}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We would welcome the opportunity to run a bid process for 2032 Olympics.\", \"from\": 6262, \"to\": 6334, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 6279, \"to\": 6294}, {\"ngram\": \"a bid process\", \"from\": 6302, \"to\": 6315}, {\"ngram\": \"2032 Olympics\", \"from\": 6320, \"to\": 6333}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The size and scale of snooker now, we could definitely lead a very strong bid.\", \"from\": 6335, \"to\": 6413, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"snooker\", \"from\": 6357, \"to\": 6364}, {\"ngram\": \"a very strong bid\", \"from\": 6395, \"to\": 6412}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It would be up to the IOC but we could make a bid for snooker alone or multi cuesports.\", \"from\": 6415, \"to\": 6503, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6438, \"end\": 6441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.799672236266796e-28, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bid\", \"from\": 6460, \"to\": 6465}, {\"ngram\": \"snooker\", \"from\": 6470, \"to\": 6477}, {\"ngram\": \"cuesports\", \"from\": 6493, \"to\": 6502}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's the problem with the current World Confederation of Billiard Sports.\", \"from\": 6504, \"to\": 6579, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the problem\", \"from\": 6511, \"to\": 6522}, {\"ngram\": \"the current World Confederation\", \"from\": 6528, \"to\": 6559}, {\"ngram\": \"Billiard Sports\", \"from\": 6563, \"to\": 6578}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The issue is there are too many factions within cue sports.\", \"from\": 6580, \"to\": 6639, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The issue\", \"from\": 6580, \"to\": 6589}, {\"ngram\": \"too many factions\", \"from\": 6603, \"to\": 6620}, {\"ngram\": \"cue sports\", \"from\": 6628, \"to\": 6638}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Look at pool, I can not even remember how many formats of pool there are and everybody wants their sport in the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 6640, \"to\": 6766, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pool\", \"f